        <h3 class="hed">Nicki Minaj, Miley Cyrus, and the VMAs: A Tone-Policing Palooza</h3>
    </a>
    <ul class="metadata">
        <li class="byline"><a href="/author/spencer-kornhaber/" title="Spencer Kornhaber">Spencer Kornhaber</a></li>
